  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-left:0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';margin-top:0px;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">sharkdp/bat</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sharkdp/bat\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/sharkdp/bat</a></span></span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">55.3k</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; License:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">Apache-2.0</span></code></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">bat 是一个带有语法高亮和 Git 集成功能的 cat(1) 命令克隆工具。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1rem;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持多种编程语言和标记语言的语法高亮显示</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">与 Git 集成，能够显示文件相对于索引的修改情况</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">可展示不可打印字符，方便调试特殊字符问题</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">自动分页输出，大文件时自动调用分页器，也支持关闭分页以模拟 cat 行为</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持多个文件拼接输出，并能在非交互式终端下作为 cat 的替代品使用</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供丰富命令行选项，如指定语言、显示行号等自定义功能</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">能与 fzf、find/fd、ripgrep 等工具集成，用于预览搜索结果或持续监控日志文件并保持高亮效果</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">兼容 git show 和 git diff，可用于查看历史版本及代码变更部分并进行语法着色</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">isaac-sim/IsaacSim</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/isaac-sim/IsaacSim\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/isaac-sim/IsaacSim</a></span></span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">1.7k</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; License:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">NOASSERTION</span></code></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">IsaacSim 是一个基于 NVIDIA Omniverse 的开源机器人仿真平台，用于在逼真的虚拟环境中开发、测试和训练 AI 驱动的机器人。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1rem;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持从 URDF、MJCF 和 CAD 等常见格式导入机器人系统及环境资产</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">利用高保真 GPU 加速物理引擎实现精确动力学模拟与多传感器 RTX 渲染</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供包括合成数据生成、强化学习、ROS 集成及数字孪生仿真在内的端到端工作流程</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">具备丰富的机器人调优工具，支持物理准确性、计算效率和光线真实感优化</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">集成了控制器、运动生成与运动学求解器等功能，方便机器人的动作模拟与策略整合</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">ByteByteGoHq/ml-bytebytego</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/ByteByteGoHq/ml-bytebytego\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ByteByteGoHq/ml-bytebytego</a></span></span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">962</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; License:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">NOASSERTION</span></code></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ml-bytebytego 是一个为系统设计面试提供参考材料的项目。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1rem;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供关于数据仓库和结构化与非结构化数据的基础知识。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">介绍集成学习中的多种技术，如 Bagging、Boosting 和 Stacking